  "original_title": "\u0baa\u0bb2 \u0b8e\u0bb0\u0bbf\u0baa\u0bca\u0bb0\u0bc1\u0bb3\u0bcd \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb0\u0baa\u0bcd\u0baa\u0bc1 \u0ba8\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bc8\u0baf\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bb3\u0bc1\u0b95\u0bcd\u0b95\u0bc1 \u0baa\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bc1",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Lock for multiple gas stations",
      "author": "T. Saranya",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Fuel Station Owners Association says many gas stations have been closed due to fuel shortages.",
        "Despite receiving the token, the public should not go to gas stations until further notice, said S. Fernando, president of the Gas Station Owners Association.",
        "He added that petrol stations will be notified of the supply of fuel as soon as it is available."
      ],
